ersion metrics (dynamic-access call sites, coverage, lines of code, dependency information).\\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:55:- Coverage collection (JaCoCo) and dynamic-access reporting per coordinate.\\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:74:- `latest/badges.json` — badges shown in the README (libraries supported, tested versions, dynamic-access coverage, tested LOC).\\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:84:1. **Add new library support** — generate a JUnit test suite, scaffold metadata, iterate until JVM-mode tests pass and dynamic-access metadata is collected.\\ndocs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:87:4. **Improve coverage** of already-supported libraries by targeting uncovered dynamic-access call sites.\\ndocs/DEVELOPING.md:319:  Output: `metadata/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/test/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\\ntests/src/org.apache.lucene/lucene-core/4.10.4/src/test/java/org_apache_lucene/lucene_core/RamUsageEstimatorTest.java:39:        BytesRef bytesRef = new BytesRef(\\\"dynamic-access\\\");\\ntests/src/org.apache.lucene/lucene-core/5.1.0/src/test/java/org_apache_lucene/lucene_core/RamUsageEstimatorTest.java:32:        BytesRef bytesRef = new BytesRef(\\\"dynamic-access\\\");\\ntests/src/org.apache.lucene/lucene-core/5.0.0/src/test/java/org_apache_lucene/lucene_core/RamUsageEstimatorTest.java:39:        BytesRef bytesRef = new BytesRef(\\\"dynamic-access\\\");\\ntests/src/org.jboss.logmanager/jboss-logmanager/1.2.0.GA/src/test/java/org_jboss_logmanager/jboss_logmanager/Formatters12Test.java:51:                \\\"Anonymous privileged-action construction is only needed for JVM dynamic-access coverage\\\");\\ntests/src/org.springframework/spring-jcl/5.3.15/src/test/java/org_springframework/spring_jcl/LogAdapterTest.java:16:    private static final String LOGGER_NAME = \\\"spring-jcl.dynamic-access\\\";\\ntests/src/io.projectreactor/reactor-core/3.5.1/src/test/java/io_projectreactor/reactor_core/TracesTest.java:20:                .checkpoint(\\\"dynamic-access-traces\\\", 